channel.title: Need start up help
channel.description:
Hey, I'm ready to publish my server. I need somebody to teamview me and help. I know very little, but nevertheless have set up my No-IP Duc, my port 43594 is forwarded, My server is on and client is open, etc. But the problem is, when I go to publish it on the server status list, it says it is offline. Another bit of help I need is, I use a client to open this, does everyone else need to, too? If so; what exactly do I upload so everyone can download it? MY BASE SERVER IS PROJECT INSANITY.
HELPPPP?
Please (: -MSN- Maddogshredder@live.com
